data.description: Welcome to this meticulously remodeled three bedroom, spa-like two and one-half bath home that sits on a double lot in Oak Forest. It has a first-floor primary bedroom with a bath and custom kitchen cabinetry, herringbone floors and marble backsplash with stainless steel appliances. The cathedral ceilings offer an open-concept view of the main floor and the custom steel staircase leads to the bedrooms with real bamboo wood floors. There is a two-car heated and air-conditioned garage with a side drive that can fit up to four cars. The siding, HVAC and water heater were brand new in 2021! This is a must-see house.
